               </u>
               <spanGrp type="Translation">
                  <span xml:lang="en" target="#URFA-002d_a5" xml:id="a12">and said, “Guys stop! I have found a solution. Let’s cut its head off and then we can take out its head.” It is said that they dragged the bull on the ground and hewed off its head.</span>
               </spanGrp>
